---
description: Trigger keyword map for canonical skills.
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

- `task-planner`: 計画, 分解, roadmap, milestone, 実装手順
- `debug-strategist`: debug, 不具合, 再現, stacktrace
- `lint-fix`: lint, format, markdownlint, prettier, yamllint
- `schema-guard`: schema, JSON検証, check-jsonschema
- `docs-sync`: README, directorystructure, technologystack, 同期
- `research-protocol`: 最新, 仕様確認, 出典
- `context-compress-map`: 要約, コンテキスト, 全体像

Each route must resolve to `.claude/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`.
